Package: raj-host
Version: 1.0.1
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Anaya Mathur <anaya@example.com>
Description: Complete Web Server Setup and Virtual Host Management Tool
 RAJ-HOST is an automated tool for setting up Nginx web servers with
 PHP-FPM, MySQL/MariaDB, and managing virtual hosts with SSL support.
 Features include:
  - Automatic installation of Nginx, PHP-FPM, MySQL/MariaDB
  - Virtual host creation with custom domain configuration
  - SSL/TLS support (Let's Encrypt and custom certificates)
  - Automatic detection of Ubuntu, Debian, CentOS, RHEL, Fedora
  - One-command setup for complete LEMP stack
Depends: bash (>= 4.0), curl
